07%2C000%2C%20per%20filings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWork%20visa%20data%20shows%20how%20much%20the%20telecom%20giant%20pays%20for%20roles%20in%20software%2C%20data%2C%20and%20networking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20helped%20shape%20the%20modern%20telecommunications%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20now%20it%20has%20to%20reinvent%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20opportunity%2C%20honestly%2C%20or%20at%20least%20once-in-a-career%20opportunity%20to%20be%20able%20to%20rebuild%20networks%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20technology%20chief%2C%20Jeremy%20Legg%2C%20said%20Monday%20at%20a%20KeyBanc%20tech%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%20a%20century%2C%20AT%26amp%3BT%20built%20and%20maintained%20a%20vast%20network%20of%20copper%20wires%20and%20dedicated%20switches%20that%20carried%20voice%20and%20data%20across%20the%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20legacy%20infrastructure%20is%20no%20longer%20suited%20to%2021st-century%20demands%20for%20speed%20and%20mobility%20that%20are%20better%20served%20by%20fiber%20optic%20networks%20and%20wireless%20spectrum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAT%26amp%3BT%20is%20now%20running%20enough%20fiber%20each%20month%20to%20reach%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20Legg%20said.%20The%20new%20network%20architecture%20is%20less%20hands-on%20and%20instead%20involves%20software-based%20solutions%20that%20are%20more%20centrally%20managed%2C%20like%20remotely%20administered%20computers%2C%20devices%2C%20or%20cloud%20servers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20competitive%20in%20the%20markets%20of%20the%20future%2C%20we%20have%20to%20change%20the%20infrastructure%20that%20we%20have%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalary%20data%20shows%20how%20much%20AT%26amp%3BT%20is%20paying%20some%20of%20the%20employees%20behind%20its%20tech%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompany%20filings%20with%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Labor%20show%20AT%26amp%3BT