.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a23a99194a2d49b8aeb3a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Original%20Tamale%20Company%20is%20located%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3Cp%3EChristian%20Ortega%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Original%20Tamale%20Company%20operates%20in%20Pacoima%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20nestled%20in%20the%20San%20Fernando%20Valley.%20Ortega%2C%20the%20owner's%20nephew%2C%20said%20his%20family%20has%20been%20in%20the%20food%20business%20for%20nearly%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20basically%20grew%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20started%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20selling%20tamales%20at%20farmers'%20markets%20and%20doing%20big%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtega%20said%20he's%20always%20been%20creative%20and%20enjoys%20making%20videos%2C%20so%20managing%20the%20restaurant's%20social%20media%20accounts%20felt%20like%20a%20natural%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20posts%20original%20content%2C%20some%20of%20his%20videos%20leverage%20popular%20memes%20or%20trends.%20The%20viral%20ad%2C%20posted%20in%20July%2C%20is%20a%20version%20of%20a%20meme%20that%20had%20been%20going%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20see%20an%20idea%20that%20I%20know%20really%20clicks%20with%20the%20company%20or%20with%20the%20audience%2C%20I%20will%20make%20something%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20and%20post%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Ortega%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtega%20said%20it's%20important%2C%20however%2C%20that%20brands%20put%20their%20personal%20spin%20on%20the%20ad.%20He%20said%20you%20must%20ask%20yourself%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20I%20make%20that%20work%20for%20my%20business%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtega%20relied%20partially%20on%20AI%20to%20create%20the%20video%2C%20including%20the%20narrator's%20voice%20and%20a%20script%20written%20by%20ChatGPT.%20However%2C%20Ortega%20typically%20tries%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20using%20AI%20and%20his%20own%20skills.%20Sometimes%2C%20he%20doesn't%20use%20AI%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20how%20people%20are%20like%2C%20'AI%20is%20sucking%20out%20all%20your%20creative%20processing%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ortega%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20AI%20as%20anything%20bad.%20I%20see%20it%20as%20a%20tool%2C%20and%20it%20definitely%20helps%20speed%20up%20the%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOrtega%20said%20the%20viral%20video%20has%20resulted%20in%20increased%20business%20at%20his%20family's%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20customers%20come%20and%20talk%20about%20the%20video%20and%20say%20that's%20the%20only%20reason%20they%20came%20because%20it%20made%20them%20laugh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20also%20because%20they%20looked%20at%20the%20reviews%2C%20and%20many%20people%20rave%20about%20the%20tamales!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BEspecially%20working%20with%20the%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-original-tamale-company-los-angeles-viral-ai-video-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755509402000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a23ae6a17a8c5b405301e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-original-tamale-company-los-angeles-viral-ai-video-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Small%20restaurants%20with%20thin%20margins%20can%20now%20make%20viral%20ads%20in%20minutes%20to%20reach%20new%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20just%20ask%20The%20Original%20Tamale%20Company%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-original-tamale-company-los-angeles-viral-ai-v