20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kairan%20Quazi%20alongside%20his%20peers%20at%20their%20graduation%20this%20week%20%20wearing%20black%20robes%20and%20red%20stoles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F648d8e1b20f78100189fdd47%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKairan%20Quazi%20alongside%20his%20peers%20at%20their%20graduation%20this%20week%3Cp%3ELisa%20Robinson%2F%20Santa%20Clara%20University%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20after%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20ever%20graduate%20of%20Santa%20Clara%20University%2C%20Quazi%20took%20his%20software%20engineering%20degree%20to%20the%20Starlink%20division%20at%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wasn't%20fetching%20coffee%20or%20working%20on%20immaterial%20projects.%20Quazi%20worked%20on%20production-critical%20systems%2C%20he%20says%2C%20designing%20and%20implementing%20software%20that%20determines%20where%20Starlink%20satellites%20target%20their%20beams%2C%20helping%20ensure%20fast%2C%20reliable%20internet%20connections%20to%20the%20company's%20millions%20of%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20very%20broad%20scope%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%2C%20especially%20for%20a%20junior%20engineer%2C%26quot%3B%20Quazi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20was%20expected%20to%20fully%20own%20projects%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bdeveloping%20ideas%20and%20presenting%20them%20to%20other%20engineers%20and%20leadership%2C%20ultimately%20implementing%20them%2C%20and%20monitoring%20the%20rollouts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20background%20and%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20a%20long%20and%20successful%20career%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20likely%20seemed%20a%20foregone%20conclusion.%20And%20at%20a%20time%20when%20many%20of%20the%20world's%20brightest%20minds%20are%20flocking%20to%20AI%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fin-silicon-valley-it-is-the-su