C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-market-tough-for-every-generation-layoffs-great-flattening-careers-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJob%20searching%20in%202025%3F%20It's%20a%20mess%20no%20matter%20how%20old%20you%20are.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-paranoia-layoffs-ai-job-security-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWelcome%20to%20the%20age%20of%20office%20paranoia%2C%20when%20layoffs%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20job%20insecurity%20are%20terrorizing%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4a295c0-e246-4a22-8460-b19d6019ec7d%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20making%20hiring%20into%20a%20technological%20cat-and-mouse%20game%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Devon%20Pastorius%20set%20out%20to%20hire%20for%20a%20new%20role%20at%20his%20advertising%20agency%2C%20he%20asked%20candidates%20to%20answer%20two%20questions%20in%20their%20cover%20letters%3A%20What%20were%20their%20thoughts%20on%20AI%20in%20the%20creative%20industry%2C%20and%20what%20were%20their%20favorite%20ads%20or%20social%20media%20accounts%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPastorius%20expected%20to%20get%20some%20AI-generated%20answers.%20What%20he%20didn't%20expect%20was%2020%20eerily%20similar%20responses%3B%20he%20surmised%20they%20came%20from%20chatbots.%20Ironically%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20first%20question%2C%20the%20AI%20answered%20that%20it%20was%20a%20tool%20and%20not%20a%20replacement%20for%20creatives.%20Its%20favorite%20ad%20campaigns%20were%20always%20Nike%20and%20Coca-Cola%2C%20and%20it%20often%20cited%20Duolingo's%20TikTok%20account%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20applicants'%20answers%20about%20the%20campaigns%20were%20also%20practically%20identical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20tracks%20with%20how%20LLMs%20work%2C%20Pastorius%20said.%20The%20AI%20scours%20the%20internet%20for%20the%20answers%20to%20a%20question%3B%20the%20brands%20that%20it%20kept%20mentioning%20have%20%26quot%3Bphenomenal%20PR%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20that%20their%20campaigns%20likely%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20coverage%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHatim%20Rahman%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20management%20and%20organizations%20at%20Northwestern%20University%2C%20said%20AI%20has%20made%20hiring%20a%20%26quot%3Bcat%20and%20mouse%20game%26quot%3B%20between%20candidates%20and%20employers%2C%20as%20both%20use%20technology%20to%20try%20to%20suss%20out%20the%20other.%20Part%20of%20that%20might%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-applications-hiring-ai-bots-spam-resume-cover-letter-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espray-and-pray%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20applicants%20use%20bots%20to%20mass-apply%20for%20jobs.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20employers%20are%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-salesforce-jobs-how-ai-evaluates-resumes-cover-letters-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20sift%20through%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterviewed-by-ai-bot-for-tech-job-pros-cons-tips-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evirtual%20agents%20step%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20interview%20prospective%20new%20hires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20escalation%20means%20it's%20harder%20for%20employers%20to%20understand%20where%20quality%20candidates%20are%2C%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20for%20prospective%20employees%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20the%20firm%20is%20like.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he's%20observed%20a%20push%20toward%20finding%20%26quot%3Bmore%20human%20signals%20in%20both%20the%20process%20of%20searching%20and%20applying%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECindy%20Meis%2C%20director%20of%20undergraduate%20career%20services%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Iowa's%20Tippie%20College%20of%20Business%2C%20said%20that%20employers%20want%20what%20she%20calls%20multiple%20touch%20points%3A%20They%20want%20to%20see%20candidates%20who%20show%20up%20and%20introduce%20and%20reintroduce%20themselves%2C%20seek%20out%20referrals%2C%20or%20do%20informational%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20keep%20going%20to%20the%20career%20fair%2C%20you%20have%20to%20go%20to%20that%20tabling%20event%20in%20order%20to%20stand%20out%20and%20reintroduce%20yourself%20to%20those%20recruiters%20and%20have%20those%20connections%20within%20the%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20Meis%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20used%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%20with%20a%20cover%20letter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20applicants%20who%20made%20it%20through%20to%20an%20interview%20with%20Pastorius%2C%20he%20made%20a%20point%20to%20ask%20follow-ups%20about%20what%20they%20wrote%20in%20their%20responses.%20And%20for%20second%20round%20interviews%2C%20he%20asks%20candidates%20to%20do%20a%20sample%20task%20at%20the%20office%20on%20a%20computer%20disconnected%20from%20the%20internet.%20That%20takes%20out%20the%20potential%20for%20AI%20interference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPastorius%20isn't%20anti-AI.%20He's%20noticed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-resume-score-helped-get-tech-job-six-figure-salary-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Er%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20formatting%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20improved.%20They're%20easier%20to%20read%2C%20and%20information%20on%20relevant%20work%20experience%20and%20skills%20was%20easy%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20ways%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20lessen%20the%20burden%20of%20job%20seeking%2C%20but%20there's%20ways%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20make%20it%20even%20harder%20on%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20Pastorius%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20parsing%20between%20the%20two%20is%20a%20skill%20within%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b20dea18-551b-48d7-867a-e158942156ce%5C%22%3EEmployers%20are%20flying%20people%20in%20and%20are%20eager%20for%20job%20hunter%20walk-ins%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVictoria%20Thomas%2C%20the%20principal%20and%20chief%20business%20officer%20of%20Kellymoss%2C%20a%20Porsche%20customization%20and%20racing%20company%2C%20adopted%20a%20new%20hiring%20practice%20in%20the%20post-pandemic%20era%20%E2%80%94%20flying%20in%20potential%20candidates%20to%20the%20company's%20Wisconsin%20office%2C%20rather%20than%20their%20previous%20reliance%20on%20phone%20or%20video%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20company%20does%20use%20AI%20to%20help%20craft%20job%20descriptions%20or%20rank%20potential%20candidates.%20But%20she's%20also%20encountered%20the%20opposite%20problem%3A%20AI-crafted%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20can%20make%20some%20candidates%20look%20stronger%20than%20they%20may%20actually%20be.%20That's%20where%20in-person%20tryouts%20come%20in.%20She's%20hiring%20for%20positions%20that%20require%20a%20lot%20of%20physical%20work%2C%20so%20it's%20important%20to%20see%20how%20potential%20candidates%20work%20with%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20very%20much%20rely%20on%20referrals%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20somebody%20that%20has%20a%20willingness%20to%20put%20their%20personal%20name%20behind%20someone%2C%20so%20a%20technician%20referring%20a%20friend%2C%20there's%20a%20larger%20success%20rate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20these%20tactile%20methods%20are%20still%20very%20much%20in%20the%20minority%2C%20but%20more%20and%20more%20companies%20might%20adopt%20them%20as%20they%20deal%20with%20firehoses%20of%20applications.%20And%20while%20they're%20easier%20to%20implement%20at%20smaller%20firms%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericas-biggest-employers-facing-great-shrinking-corporations-ai-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeath%20of%20the%20mega-employer%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20mean%20smaller%20companies%20are%20increasingly%20the%20future%20for%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENastashia%20Wali%2C%20the%20director%20of%20front%20office%20at%20the%20storied%20Hotel%20Chelsea%2C%20said%20that%20a%20candidate%20showing%20up%20in%20person%20demonstrates%20%26quot%3Beagerness%20and%20extra%20effort.%26quot%3B%20Online%20applications%20have%20meant%20more%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20so%20she%20needs%20more%20patience%20to%20sift%20through%20potential%20candidates.%20Wali%20said%20that%20she%20likes%20receiving%20paper%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20%E2%80%94%20it%20lets%20candidates%20make%20a%20first%20impression%20on%20her%20front%20desk%20team%2C%20who%20bring%20their%20insights%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20team%20gives%20me%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20ask%20is%20what%20stood%20out%20about%20the%20candidate%20and%20how%20their%20demeanor%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20team%20notices%20something%2C%20I%20usually%20pick%20up%20on%20it%20too%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20seemed%20off%2C%20friendly%20and%20talkative%2C%20or%20made%20any%20other%20distinct%20impression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-process-ai-paper-resumes-in-person-job-interviews-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1755503762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f5da5194a2d49b8aea564%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-process-ai-paper-resumes-in-person-job-interviews-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20hiring%20process%20exhausted%20by%20AI%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20apply%20to%20jobs%20like%20it's%201999.%20Old-school%20paper%20resumes%20and%20in-person%20interviews%20are%20back.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jkaplan%40businessinsider.com%20(Juliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-process-ai-paper-resumes-in-person-job-interviews-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22