n't%20live%20here%3B%20you%20work%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20left%20a%20mark%20on%20me.%20I%20remember%20thinking%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20visa%20has%20become%20a%20consideration%20in%20my%20family%20planning%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%2030%2C%20and%20I%20have%20been%20looking%20into%20egg%20freezing%20as%20an%20option.%20While%20researching%20the%20process%2C%20I%20thought%20about%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20I%20no%20longer%20had%20working%20rights%20in%20the%20US%20and%20wanted%20to%20retrieve%20the%20eggs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20this%20vision%20of%20rolling%20into%20the%20US%20on%20a%20tourist%20visa%20with%20a%20suitcase%20to%20pick%20up%20my%20eggs%2C%20and%20I%20thought%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20worth%20it.%26quot%3B%20I%20also%20can't%20imagine%20having%20a%20person%20depend%20on%20me%20while%20I'm%20on%20a%20temporary%20status%20tied%20to%20having%20a%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20year%2C%20I%20sit%20down%20and%20have%20a%20check-in%20with%20myself.%20I%20take%20into%20account%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20and%20the%20anxiety%20I%20feel%20about%20the%20future%2C%20and%20ask%20myself%20if%20this%20is%20still%20worth%20it.%20The%20answer%20has%20been%20yes%20%E2%80%94%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20days%20I%20feel%20anxious%2C%20I%20try%20to%20refocus%20on%20the%20things%20in%20my%20control.%20I%20also%20have%20a%20decent%20financial%20cushion%20by%20now%2C%20which%20is%20another%20benefit%20of%20working%20in%20tech%20in%20the%20US%20for%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20a%20project%20on%20the%20experiences%20of%20Indian%20H-1B%20holders%20working%20in%20tech.%20Read%20the%20full%20story%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh-1b-visa-big-tech-immigration-green-card-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3