hat%20helps%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F275931%2Fkerala-couple-shinod-bindhu-donate-earnings-to-monthly-welfare-scheme-for-poor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamilies%20trapped%20in%20generational%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E%20become%20self-reliant%20in%20300%20days.%20Tetari%20joined%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago%2C%20and%20the%20transformation%20has%20been%20more%20than%20just%20financial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20go%20to%20the%20market%20or%20how%20to%20talk%20to%20customers.%20But%20they%20taught%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20now%2033-year-old.%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20I%20earn%20Rs%2010%2C000%20every%20month.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECan%20you%20really%20end%20poverty%20for%20someone%20in%2030%20days%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20homes%20across%20India%2C%20financial%20precarity%20is%20an%20uninvited%20guest.%20The%20Leap%20300%20team%20saw%20it%20often%20%E2%80%94%20pulling%20up%20a%20chair%20at%20dinner%2C%20raising%20its%20eyebrows%20if%20someone%20dared%20take%20an%20extra%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flatbread)%2C%20delivering%20sharp%20retorts%20when%20a%20family%20member%20voiced%20their%20aspirations%2C%20and%20wearing%20a%20mask%20of%20scepticism%20at%20any%20promise%20of%20a%20better%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinod%20Raghuwanshi%20is%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20has%20developed%20the%20Leap%20300%20app%2C%20which%20claims%20to%20have%20helped%20375%20families%20out%20of%20poverty.%20He%20explains%20there%20are%20three%20ways%20of%20tackling%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20way%20is%20to%20skill%20people%20until%20they%20become%20employable%3B%20the%20other%20is%20providing%20them%20with%20assets%20that