%20pledges%20we%20have%20so%20often%20taken%20and%20the%20one%20we%20shall%20take%20today.%20The%20service%20of%20India%20means%20the%20service%20of%20the%20millions%20who%20suffer.%20It%20means%20the%20ending%20of%20poverty%20and%20ignorance%20and%20disease%2C%20and%20inequality%20of%20opportunity.%20The%20ambition%20of%20the%20greatest%20man%20of%20our%20generation%20has%20been%20to%20wipe%20every%20tear%20from%20every%20eye.%20That%20may%20be%20beyond%20us%2C%20but%20as%20long%20as%20there%20are%20tears%20and%20suffering%2C%20so%20long%20our%20work%20will%20not%20be%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20we%20have%20to%20labour%20and%20work%2C%20and%20work%20hard%2C%20to%20give%20reality%20to%20our%20dreams.%20Those%20dreams%20are%20for%20India%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20for%20the%20world%2C%20for%20all%20the%20nations%20and%20peoples%20are%20too%20closely%20knit%20together%20today%20for%20any%20one%20of%20them%20to%20imagine%20that%20it%20can%20live%20apart%20Peace%20has%20been%20said%20to%20be%20indivisible%3B%20so%20is%20freedom%2C%20so%20is%20prosperity%20now%2C%20and%20so%20also%20is%20disaster%20in%20this%20One%20World%20that%20can%20no%20longer%20be%20split%20into%20isolated%20fragments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2F3_11zon-2-1754921606.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20spirit%20of%20optimism%20and%20determination%20rang%20through%20his%20words%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2F3_11zon-2-1754921606.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2F3_11zon-2-1754921606-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2F3_11zon-2-1754921606-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.